These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, february, october
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, havana, montecristo, swisher
City: paris, new-york, edinburgh, berlin
 1. the havana-smoker is not to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 2. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
 3. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8
 5. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person traveling to new-york and the havana-smoker##2
 9. the person traveling to berlin is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
12. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
14. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
15. the person who's birthday is in september is not the havana-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday         | july     | september   | october | february |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk   | milk   | hot-chocolate  |
| Cigar         | havana  | montecristo  | swisher  | bluemaster |
| City     | paris    | edinburgh | new-york     | berlin    |

