.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, french, russian, australian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, blend, vegafina
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, architect, lawyer, coach
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, woodworking, collecting
 1. the lawyer is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the architect##2
 2. the french is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 3. the french is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 4. the italian is not to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the architect##8
 6. the vegafina-smoker is not to the right of the australian##8
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 9. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the lawyer##8
12. the australian is on the left of the french##1
13. the coach is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
14. the architect is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
15. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
16. the blend-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
17. the italian is not to the right of the architect##8
18. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
19. the australian is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Nationality      | italian | russian | australian  | french  |
| Cigar          | vegafina     | pall-mall | ritmeester | blend  |
| Job   | architect    | lawyer  | coach | mechanic |
| Hobby           | woodworking | collecting | magic-tricks    | card-games  |

