 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
 6. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
 7. the palace house is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the colonial house##8
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3

