4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, fish, frog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, action, drama, sports
 1. the cottage house is not the owner of the rabbit##6
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the fish##1
 4. the person who likes amber is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 5. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the right of the person who likes amber##8
 7. the modern house is in an odd position##4
 8. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
 9. the modern house is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
10. the owner of the hamster is the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person who likes red##8
12. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
13. the cottage house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
14. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
15. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
