10. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the person who growsmarigold##8
11. the photographer is between the person who likes coral and the person who growsamaryllis##2
12. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the accountant##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
