.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, action, sports, family
House: cottage, futuristic, craftsman, tower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, baseball, tennis
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, corn, broccoli, potato
 1. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
 2. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the tower house##8
 3. the person eating cucumber is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 4. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching family movies##5
 5. the person eating broccoli is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person who's sport is golf##8
 7. the person watching action movies is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
 8. the futuristic house is somewhere between the person eating broccoli and the person watching action movies##7
 9. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
10. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
11. the craftsman house is on the right of the cottage house##1
12. the futuristic house is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
13. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
14. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
15. the person eating cucumber is not to the right of the futuristic house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | action    | family   | sports        | spy  |
| House           | tower     | futuristic | cottage | craftsman  |
| Sport   | snowboarding | tennis    | baseball   | golf     |
| Food     | potato       | cucumber     | broccoli    | corn |

