There 4 different types of food: zucchini, strawberry, raspberry, cabbage
 1. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
 2. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 4. the manager is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 6. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 7. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's birthday is in august##7
10. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the firefighter##8
11. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
12. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
14. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
