There are 4 different nationalities: american, russian, chinese, turkish
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, bridge, poker
 1. the russian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 2. the person playing backgammon is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
 3. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
 4. the chinese is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 7. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
 8. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is sailing##7
 9. the american is on the far left or far right##3
10. the russian is not to the left of the russian##8
11. the american is on the far left##1
12. the turkish is on the far right##1
13. the person playing poker is the person who's sport is badminton##1
14. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
15. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
16. the russian is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8

.:: Answer ::.
