4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, pony, cat
4 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, go, monopoly
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, amber, ivory, black
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 2. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is not the person who likes ivory##6
 4. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
 8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##8
10. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
11. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person who likes ivory##8
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
13. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing go and the person who likes white##2
14. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |    4    |
