.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-15::.
City: paris, colone, edinburgh, berlin
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, begonia, daffodil, rose
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, water, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, baking, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to berlin##5
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 6. the person traveling to berlin is the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
10. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
14. the person traveling to colone is not to the right of the person traveling to berlin##8
15. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsdaffodil##1
16. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| City           | edinburgh | colone       | paris      | berlin  |
