.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, domino, chess
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, photography, singing, camping
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, bird, cat
City: berlin, hamburg, boston, venice
 1. the person playing domino is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing chess##1
12. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
