4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, bluemaster, chaman
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
 4. the person playing billiard is the wooden house##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is not the person playing chess##6
 6. the victorian house is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
 7. the craftsman house is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 8. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 9. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
10. the victorian house is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
11. the victorian house is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking sprite is between the person playing chess and the person drinking almond-milk##2
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk    | sprite   | juice   | cola |
| Game           | whist | scrabble    | chess | billiard    |
| House   | cape-cod   | victorian | craftsman     | wooden    |
| Cigar   | dunhill   | bluemaster      | blend         | chaman     |

 